    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《诸神竞技场》是一款策略丰富的快节奏PVP卡牌游戏，游戏中拥有四大神话体系（华夏、希腊、埃及、北欧）的51位神灵，以及丰富多样的武器、装备、技能卡等123种构筑卡供你选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在1v1、2v2、身份战、势力战、肉鸽PVE模式中，玩家可以根据自己的喜好和策略，从海量卡牌中挑选合适的卡牌，构建属于自己的独特卡组。同时，还可以根据不同的对战场景和对手，灵活调整卡组，创造出千变万化的战术策略，展现自己的个性与智慧，运筹帷幄，与其他玩家一决高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/095b9e8526b1e7d6b9d2787124d6d9c0.avif?t=1766543766\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras_big/095b9e8526b1e7d6b9d2787124d6d9c0.avif?t=1766543766 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四大文明 诸神争霸</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内以华夏、北欧、希腊、埃及四大文明神灵为主题，拥有高达53位神灵供您选择，有埃及金字塔下的阿努比斯、北欧冰原挥舞雷神之锤的索尔、希腊以智慧守护队友的雅典娜、更有华夏孙悟空七十二变尽显神通。每个文明都有独特的神灵、构筑卡和故事，玩家可以收集来自不同文明的神灵及卡牌，组建属于自己的多元卡组，感受不同文明的碰撞与融合，体验跨越时空的奇妙之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/e0ee066ba3c0fc1e3cb8062625047df8.poster.avif?t=1766543766\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/e0ee066ba3c0fc1e3cb8062625047df8.webm?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/e0ee066ba3c0fc1e3cb8062625047df8.mp4?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >跨平台对战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打破平台限制，无论是在手机、平板还是电脑上，玩家都可以与所有玩家实时对战。随时随地与全服玩家一较高下，展示自己的策略才华，结交志同道合的朋友，共同探索游戏的无限可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/b8cd267f612c81fac7a7595ec4695e2f.poster.avif?t=1766543766\" width=640 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/b8cd267f612c81fac7a7595ec4695e2f.webm?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/b8cd267f612c81fac7a7595ec4695e2f.mp4?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爽快连击玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中独特的连击系统，让玩家在战斗中可以通过合理出牌实现爽快的连击效果。当玩家成功打出连击时，不仅能对敌人造成巨大的伤害，还能触发各种神灵技能与构筑卡效果，体验畅快淋漓的战斗快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/7f4a2d60ec87ad37cc04e5ed65e7d581.poster.avif?t=1766543766\" width=640 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/7f4a2d60ec87ad37cc04e5ed65e7d581.webm?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/7f4a2d60ec87ad37cc04e5ed65e7d581.mp4?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多场景模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供丰富的对战场景，包括紧张刺激的 1v1 单挑对决，考验个人的策略与技巧；默契配合的 2v2 组队对战，需要与队友密切协作，共同制定战术；还有充满挑战的 PVE 模式，玩家可以挑战强大的对手，探索神秘的关卡，体验精彩的剧情。不同的场景模式满足了玩家不同的游戏需求，让玩家在游戏中体验到更多的乐趣和挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/648007446edd8d18c3dafbcb721b2bb4.poster.avif?t=1766543766\" width=640 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/648007446edd8d18c3dafbcb721b2bb4.webm?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/648007446edd8d18c3dafbcb721b2bb4.mp4?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Steam独家赛事竞技系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam将举办独家赛事——全民智斗赛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/0aed428d3ed873df9bd79448a242b402.poster.avif?t=1766543766\" width=640 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/0aed428d3ed873df9bd79448a242b402.webm?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065580/extras/0aed428d3ed873df9bd79448a242b402.mp4?t=1766543766\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏攻略，游戏赛事内容，可通过以下方式关注：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏攻略站</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BWIKI：</strong>@诸神竞技场</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注官方赛事动态</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>官方Q群：</strong>929477406</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>官方B站账号：</strong>@诸神竞技场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
